Demonstrate a PHP script which rounds the following values with 1 decimal digit precision.
Sample values : 1.65 1.65 -1.54

CODE:
<?php
// Sample values
$values = [1.65, 1.65, -1.54];

// Round each value to 1 decimal place
foreach ($values as $num) {
    $rounded = round($num, 1);
    echo "Original: $num  -->  Rounded: $rounded<br>";
}
?>

OUTPUT:
Original: 1.65  -->  Rounded: 1.7
Original: 1.65  -->  Rounded: 1.7
Original: -1.54  -->  Rounded: -1.5
